            <div class="field field--title field--name-node-title field--type-ds field--label-hidden field--item"><h3>
  <a href="/fashion-clothing/shopping-guide/high-street-clothes-shops" hreflang="en">High Street Clothes Shops</a>
</h3>
</div>
      
    
    <p>
      In this guide, we investigate, score and rank the ethical and environmental record of 52&nbsp;high street brands.
We also look at the problem with fast fashion, workers' rights, shine a light on the ethics of Boohoo, Shein, and Temu, look at sustainable fabrics, delve into greenwashing, and give some recommended buys.
    </p>
