  </picture>

    </div>

</a></div>
      
      </div>
        
    
            <div class="field field--title field--name-node-title field--type-ds field--label-hidden field--item"><h3>
  <a href="/fashion-clothing/shopping-guide/ethical-outdoor-clothing" hreflang="en">Ethical outdoor clothing</a>
</h3>
</div>
      
    
    <p>
      Rating 41 brands of outdoor clothing and gear for their ethics and sustainability.&nbsp;
We look at the environmental impact of synthetic materials and toxic chemicals, animal rights and workers' rights. We also look at repair options for a more sustainable approach, vegan outdoor clothing, and put Berghaus against North Face in an ethical head to head.
    </p>
    <a href="/fashion-clothing/shopping-guide/ethical-outdoor-clothing" class="btn btn-ecra btn-link nowrap">
      Read more<span class="visually-hidden"> about 
            
  Ethical outdoor clothing


      </span><i class="fa fa-arrow-circle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </a>
  </div>
</article>


